      <title>Sriram：年底通胀放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-26/see-inflation-decelerating-through-year-end-sriram-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱美国经济学家普贾·斯里拉姆 (Pooja Sriram) 认为，今年剩余时间通胀可能继续放缓，宏观经济背景也将逐渐放缓。她与彭博社的乔纳森·费罗和丽莎·阿布拉莫维奇就“彭博监控”进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-26/see-inflation-decelerating-through-year-end-sriram-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 17:38:25 GMT</pubDate>
